            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/1582425/">《女人不坏》，人见人爱</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1582425_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1582425">
                    <div class="short-content">

                           看完《女人不坏》的整整24个小时，我仍然无法在下过初雪的北京寒冬中冷静下来，内心澎湃、面若桃红等种种生理迹象表明我对徐克制造的费洛蒙反应成功，彻底失掉了一个自诩深邃客观的严肃影评人姿态。     某个时间、某个地点、某首音乐、某杯咖啡，某个撩拨的姿态、某缕发丝...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1582425-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1582425_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1582425_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1582425" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1582425">
                                191
                        </span>
